#. DIALOGUE_PODUNK_CUTSCENES_PIPPI_REUNITE_0
msgid "[@]Sigh... She's not here either..."
msgstr "[@]嘶...她也不在这..."

#. DIALOGUE_PODUNK_CUTSCENES_PIPPI_REUNITE_3
msgid "[@]Mom?"
msgstr "[@]妈妈？"

#. DIALOGUE_PODUNK_CUTSCENES_PIPPI_REUNITE_4
msgid "[@][Pippi]...?[WAIT@]Is that you?"
msgstr "[@][Pippi]...？[WAIT@]是你吗？"

#. DIALOGUE_PODUNK_CUTSCENES_PIPPI_REUNITE_6
msgid "[@]Yup!"
msgstr "[@]是的！"

#. DIALOGUE_PODUNK_CUTSCENES_PIPPI_REUNITE_7
msgid "[@]Oh, what a relief![WAIT@]I thought I lost you forever...[WAIT@]Where in the world did you wander off to this time?"
msgstr "[@]哦，真是松了口气！[WAIT@]我以为我永远失去了你...[WAIT@]这次你究竟到哪儿去了？"

#. DIALOGUE_PODUNK_CUTSCENES_PIPPI_REUNITE_10
msgid "[@]You won't believe it, but I was chasing a butterfly when suddenly, some zombies kidnapped me!"
msgstr "[@]你肯定不信，我正在追一只蝴蝶，突然， 一些丧尸绑架了我！"

#. DIALOGUE_PODUNK_CUTSCENES_PIPPI_REUNITE_11
msgid "[@]Really?"
msgstr "[@]真的吗？"

#. DIALOGUE_PODUNK_CUTSCENES_PIPPI_REUNITE_12
msgid "[@]Yeah! They even locked me in a coffin!"
msgstr "[@]真的！他们甚至还把我锁在棺材里！"

#. DIALOGUE_PODUNK_CUTSCENES_PIPPI_REUNITE_13
msgid "[@]That must have been terrifying!"
msgstr "[@]那一定很可怕！"

#. DIALOGUE_PODUNK_CUTSCENES_PIPPI_REUNITE_14
msgid "[@]Eh, not really. It was kind of cozy actually."
msgstr "[@]嗯，不完全是。[DELAY]实际上还挺舒服的。"

#. DIALOGUE_PODUNK_CUTSCENES_PIPPI_REUNITE_15
msgid "[@]And I assume it was [Ninten] over there that saved you, right?"
msgstr "[@]我猜是那边的[Ninten]救了你，对吧？"

#. DIALOGUE_PODUNK_CUTSCENES_PIPPI_REUNITE_16
msgid "[@]Hmm, I guess you could say that."
msgstr "[@]呣，可以那么说。"

#. DIALOGUE_PODUNK_CUTSCENES_PIPPI_REUNITE_17
msgid "[@]Oh, I knew I could count on you to save my precious [Pippi]."
msgstr "[@]哦，我就知道我可以指望你来救我的宝贝[Pippi]。"

#. DIALOGUE_PODUNK_CUTSCENES_PIPPI_REUNITE_18
msgid "[@]Thank you, [Ninten]. You truly are a hero."
msgstr "[@]谢谢你，[Ninten]。你真是个英雄。"

#. DIALOGUE_PODUNK_CUTSCENES_PIPPI_REUNITE_19
msgid "[@]Say mom, you mind helping us with something?"
msgstr "[@]妈妈，你能帮我们个忙吗？"

#. DIALOGUE_PODUNK_CUTSCENES_PIPPI_REUNITE_20
msgid "[@]Yeah, sure! What is it?"
msgstr "[@]好的，当然！什么忙？"

#. DIALOGUE_PODUNK_CUTSCENES_PIPPI_REUNITE_21
msgid "[@]You see... This poor birdie got lost and we're trying to find its mommy."
msgstr "[@]你看...这只可怜的小鸟走丢了，我们正在找它的妈妈。"

#. DIALOGUE_PODUNK_CUTSCENES_PIPPI_REUNITE_22
msgid "[@]Have you seen her?"
msgstr "[@]你们见过它的妈妈吗？"

#. DIALOGUE_PODUNK_CUTSCENES_PIPPI_REUNITE_23
msgid "[@]Oh! That must be singing Laura's baby![WAIT@]She's so sad, she's hardly showing herself to anyone these days."
msgstr "[@]哦！那一定是鸣鸟Laura的孩子！[WAIT@]她很伤心，这些天几乎不露面。"

#. DIALOGUE_PODUNK_CUTSCENES_PIPPI_REUNITE_25
msgid "[@]I don't know where she is now, but I do know [color]she's still somewhere on this island[/color]."
msgstr "[@]我不知道她在哪里，但是我知道[color]她还在这个岛上的某个地方[/color]。"

#. DIALOGUE_PODUNK_CUTSCENES_PIPPI_REUNITE_26
msgid "[@]If you need anything else, feel free to ask me."
msgstr "[@]如果你还需要什么，尽管问我。"

#. DIALOGUE_PODUNK_CUTSCENES_PIPPI_REUNITE_27
msgid "[@]Okay thanks, mom!"
msgstr "[@]好的谢谢，妈妈！"

#. DIALOGUE_PODUNK_CUTSCENES_PIPPI_REUNITE_SPEAKER_???
msgid "???"
msgstr "？？？"

#. DIALOGUE_PODUNK_CUTSCENES_PIPPI_REUNITE_SPEAKER_Mrs._Lindgren
msgid "Mrs. Lindgren"
msgstr "Mrs. Lindgren"

#. DIALOGUE_PODUNK_CUTSCENES_PIPPI_TOWN_HALL_CANARY_0
msgid "[@]Hey! We're supposed to deliver this canary to its mom, remember?[WAIT@]Canary Village is at the northwest of town.[WAIT@]Come on, let's go!"
msgstr "[@]嘿！我们应该把这只金丝雀交给它妈妈，还记得吗？[WAIT@]金丝雀村在城镇的西北部。[WAIT@]来吧，我们走吧！"

#. DIALOGUE_PODUNK_CUTSCENES_PIPPI_TOWN_HALL_REJECT_0
msgid "[@]Hey, why are we going to the town hall?[WAIT@]Isn't that place boring?[WAIT@]Come on, let's go somewhere else![WAIT@]How about the [color]department store[/color]?[WAIT@]I hear they have a new animal at the [color]pet shop[/color] there!"
msgstr "[@]喂，我们去市政厅干嘛呀？[WAIT@] 那地方不是很无聊吗？[WAIT@] 拜托，咱们换个地方去吧！[WAIT@] 去[color]百货商店[/color]怎么样？[WAIT@] 我听说那儿的[color]宠物店[/color]新来一只小动物呢！"

#. DIALOGUE_PODUNK_CUTSCENES_PIPPISMOM_CALL_0
msgid "[@][Pippi]!"
msgstr "[@][Pippi]!"

#. DIALOGUE_PODUNK_CUTSCENES_PIPPISMOM_CALL_1
msgid "[@]Oh, [Pippi]!"
msgstr "[@]哦，[Pippi]！"

#. DIALOGUE_PODUNK_CUTSCENES_PIPPISMOM_CALL_2
msgid "[@]Oh me, oh my!"
msgstr "[@]我的天，我的天！"

#. DIALOGUE_PODUNK_CUTSCENES_PIPPISMOM_CALL_3
msgid "[@]Oh me, oh my!"
msgstr "[@]我的天，我的天！"

#. DIALOGUE_PODUNK_CUTSCENES_PIPPISMOM_CALL_4
msgid "[@]What can I do, what should I do?!"
msgstr "[@]我能做什么，我应该做什么?!"

#. DIALOGUE_PODUNK_CUTSCENES_PIPPISMOM_CALL_SPEAKER_Mrs._Lindgren
msgid "Mrs. Lindgren"
msgstr "Mrs. Lindgren"

#. DIALOGUE_PODUNK_CUTSCENES_PIPPISMOM_HELP_1
msgid "[@]Oh, hello [Ninten]..."
msgstr "[@]哦，你好[Ninten]..."

#. DIALOGUE_PODUNK_CUTSCENES_PIPPISMOM_HELP_4
msgid "[@]It seems my dear [color][Pippi][/color]'s gone missing![WAIT@]She always goes outside to play, but she hasn't come home since yesterday...[WAIT@]If you're going into town, please ask [color]Mayor Goodman[/color] if anyone's seen her, okay?"
msgstr "[@]我心爱的[color][Pippi][/color]好像不见了！[WAIT@] 她总爱跑到外面去玩，可从昨天起就再也没回过家...[WAIT@] 你要是要进城的话，麻烦帮我问问[color]好人市长[/color]，看有没有人见过她，好吗？"

#. DIALOGUE_PODUNK_CUTSCENES_PIPPISMOM_HELP_7
msgid "[@](Sniffle sniffle... Sob sob...)"
msgstr "[@]（抽泣...抽泣...）"

#. DIALOGUE_PODUNK_CUTSCENES_PIPPISMOM_HELP_9
msgid "[@]Yes, you will?"
msgstr "[@]是的，你会？"

#. DIALOGUE_PODUNK_CUTSCENES_PIPPISMOM_HELP_10
msgid "[@]Thank you so much, [Ninten]!"
msgstr "[@]非常感谢你，[Ninten]！"

#. DIALOGUE_PODUNK_CUTSCENES_PIPPISMOM_HELP_SPEAKER_Mrs._Lindgren
msgid "Mrs. Lindgren"
msgstr "Mrs. Lindgren"

#. DIALOGUE_PODUNK_CUTSCENES_STARMAN_JR_ATTACK_2
msgid "[@]I'm surprised that a human child such as yourself has managed to get here...[WAIT@]More surprising however, is that my analysis indicates that you possess the ability to harness PSI.[WAIT@]While those powers seem to have only awakened recently, you appear to be quite skilled at using them.[WAIT@]If left unchecked, they could prove themselves to be a problem...[WAIT@]We must not allow someone like you to interfere with our plans."
msgstr "[@] 真没想到，你这样的人类小孩竟能一路闯到这里……[WAIT@]更令人意外的是，我的分析显示，你拥有操控灵能的潜质。[WAIT@]虽说这份力量似乎才刚觉醒不久，你运用起来却相当娴熟。[WAIT@]若是放任不管，日后定会成为我们的隐患...[WAIT@]绝不能让你这样的人，妨碍我们的计划。"

#. DIALOGUE_PODUNK_CUTSCENES_STARMAN_JR_ATTACK_7
msgid "[@]You may have bested the vicious beasts of this place, but you are no match to me!"
msgstr "[@]你也许打败了这里的恶兽，但你绝对不是我的对手！"

#. DIALOGUE_PODUNK_CUTSCENES_STARMAN_JR_ATTACK_REMATCH_2
msgid "[@]No matter how many times you come back, you will never beat me!"
msgstr "[@]不管你回来多少次，你永远也打不过我！"

#. DIALOGUE_PODUNK_CUTSCENES_STARMAN_JR_DEFEAT_1
msgid "[@]Impossible... I can't believe that I've been defeated by a mere human child...[WAIT@]I'll have to report this incident to the mothership..."
msgstr "[WAIT@]不可能...我不敢相信我竟然被一个人类小孩打败了...[WAIT@]我得把这件事报告给母舰..."

#. DIALOGUE_PODUNK_CUTSCENES_STARMAN_JR_DEFEAT_7
msgid "[@]The odd sound that drove the animals insane died down."
msgstr "[@]这些动物发疯的奇怪声音渐渐消失了。"

#. DIALOGUE_PODUNK_CUTSCENES_STARMAN_JR_DEFEAT_8
msgid "[@]The Zoo became a safe place once more."
msgstr "[@]动物园变安全了。"

#. DIALOGUE_PODUNK_CUTSCENES_WALLY_ATTACK_1_0
msgid "[@]Who's there?!"
msgstr "[@]谁在哪?!"

#. DIALOGUE_PODUNK_CUTSCENES_WALLY_ATTACK_1_3
msgid "[@]Uh oh, it's Wally!"
msgstr "[@]啊哦，是Wally！"

#. DIALOGUE_PODUNK_CUTSCENES_WALLY_ATTACK_1_4
msgid "[@]Hey, I recognize that little ginger face!"
msgstr "[@]嘿，我认得那张姜黄色的小脸！"

#. DIALOGUE_PODUNK_CUTSCENES_WALLY_ATTACK_1_5
msgid "[@]You're that kid who's been eating all my flowers!"
msgstr "[@]你是那个吃光了我的花的孩子！"

#. DIALOGUE_PODUNK_CUTSCENES_WALLY_ATTACK_1_6
msgid "[@]Well excuuuse me, but there weren't any signs telling me NOT to eat them."
msgstr "[@]拜托原谅我吧，没有任何标志告诉我不要吃它们。"

#. DIALOGUE_PODUNK_CUTSCENES_WALLY_ATTACK_1_7
msgid "[@]Also, they weren't that good anyway..."
msgstr "[@]而且，他们也没那么好吃..."

#. DIALOGUE_PODUNK_CUTSCENES_WALLY_ATTACK_1_8
msgid "[@]GRRR! I've had enough!"
msgstr "[@]啊啊啊！我受够了！"

